729928f-a.title: Richmond: Windemere Road - Fingerboard Road
729928f-a.text:
(1)
Windemere Road (houses thereon), between Finger-
board Road and Clove Road, seen across Camerons Pond. This
area is part of the former large Sir Roderick Cameron estate.
April 22, 1932
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, another view.
April 22, 1932
P. L. Sperr
